					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The PlayChoice-10 does use the same palette, mostly - it is missing the grays at $1D/$2D/$3D, and color emphasis works completely differently, forcing each channel to maximum intensity (which can cause problems in some games which set all 3 bits, expecting to dim the screen by 25% but instead resulting in a solid white screen).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
